You must be 10 years of age or older to play Seal Runners. By using the Game, you confirm that you meet this age requirement.

2. User Conduct
By playing Seal Runners, you agree not to engage in any behavior that could negatively impact the experience of other players or the integrity of the Game. The following actions are strictly prohibited:

Discriminatory Behavior: No racism, homophobia, transphobia, sexism, or hate speech of any kind.
Toxicity: No harassment, threats, bullying, or inflammatory behavior.
Exploiting: No use of bugs, glitches, or unintended mechanics to gain an advantage or disrupt gameplay.
Map Exploits: No glitching out of or beyond the playable map areas.
Impersonation: Do not impersonate moderators, staff, or developers.
Begging or Soliciting: Do not ask for in-game items, cosmetics, or moderator privileges.
Username Policy: You must set a valid, non-offensive username upon joining. Empty, misleading, or offensive names are not permitted.
Objectionable Content: Do not display or share sexually explicit, violent, or inappropriate content.
Unauthorized Modifications: Use of cheats, mods, or third-party software that alters gameplay or network traffic is prohibited.
Voice & Chat Etiquette: All in-game communication must be respectful and appropriate for all players.

3. Account Responsibility
You are solely responsible for all actions taken on your account or device. If someone else uses your VR headset and violates these Terms, the consequences will still apply to your account. No exceptions will be made for shared or borrowed devices. No unbans will be given under these circumstances.

